---
// src/components/Hero.astro
---

<section id="hero" class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center overflow-hidden bg-black">
  <!-- Video Background with DNA animation -->
  <video autoplay muted loop playsinline class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-40">
    <source src="/video/dna.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
  </video>
  
  <!-- Gradient Overlay -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-black via-blue-900/80 to-black z-10"></div>
  
  <!-- Main Content -->
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 relative z-20">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center">
      <div class="md:w-3/5 text-white space-y-6 md:pr-12">
        <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-blue-600/30 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-full border border-blue-400/30 mb-4">
          <p class="text-blue-200 text-sm font-medium">Microbioma • Inteligência Artificial • Bioinformática</p>
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold leading-tight">
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 via-blue-300 to-white bg-clip-text text-transparent">
            Decisões Inteligentes para uma Produção Animal Mais Rentável
          </span>
        </h1>
        
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-xl">
          Com IA aplicada ao microbioma, a AlphaBioma transforma análises genéticas em soluções que melhoram a saúde, o desempenho e a rentabilidade do seu rebanho.
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 pt-4">
          <a href="#contact" class="px-6 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-800 to-blue-600 text-white font-medium rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-blue-600/20 transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
            Iniciar Projeto
          </a>
          <a href="#services" class="px-6 py-3 border border-white/30 backdrop-blur-sm bg-white/10 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-white/20 transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
            Conhecer Serviços
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Right side floating visuals -->
      <div class="hidden md:block md:w-2/5 relative">
        <div class="absolute top-10 right-10 w-64 h-64 rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 animate-pulse"></div>
        <div class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-900/40 to-blue-700/20 backdrop-blur-md p-6 rounded-2xl border border-blue-500/20 shadow-xl transform rotate-2 hover:rotate-0 transition-all duration-500 w-full max-w-md">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center bg-blue-600/30">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-200" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Análise de Microbioma</h3>
          </div>
          
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-white/90">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-300 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Microbioma personalizado</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-300 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Conectando dados genéticos e desempenho</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-300 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Redução do uso de antibióticos com saúde intestinal</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Scroll indicator -->
    <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 z-10 animate-bounce hidden md:block">
      <a href="#MicrobiomeIntro" class="text-white flex flex-col items-center">
        <span class="text-sm mb-2 text-blue-200">Saiba mais</span>
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-300" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>